        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7241",
        "content": "\"Very little,\" replied the cat.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7241_90852_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7241/90852/7241_90852_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7241",
        "content": "Now Zidoc knew very well where the dog had concealed himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7241_90852_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7241/90852/7241_90852_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7241",
        "content": "First, Zidoc locked the only door with a great key and then he said to Serponel,--",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7241_90852_000047_000000",
